        "client_msg_id": "27332763-9b18-4667-8f85-950e43048c80",
        "text": "There's no single practice or way of getting to a profitable strategy. What may work for a syndicate may not work for you and viceversa just because the details are usually many. You can definitely start from the lambdas but it's a one score per the entire team over multiple matches, you will need to refine from there.",
